com.github.kskelm.baringo

  • Packages that use com.github.kskelm.baringo 
    Package Description
    com.github.kskelm.baringo

  • Classes in com.github.kskelm.baringo used by com.github.kskelm.baringo 
    Class and Description
    AccountService
    Manages the user's account, settings, favorites, etc
    AlbumService
    Manages albums.
    AuthService
    Manages the API's authentication for a specific user.
    BaringoClient
    The Baringo client that is the foundation for all API calls to Imgur
    BaringoClient.Builder
    This is used to construct a new BaringoClient
    CommentService
    Manages comments, which can be attached to images and albums.
    CommentService.CommentListWrapper
    Imgur's Json serializer-- like many-- doesn't know when it should be generating an array if it only finds one item in a list so instead of an array with one item, it just generates the item as an object, and parsers the whole world over break.
    ConversationService
    Manages messages between users
    CustomGalleryService
    Provides control over a user's custom gallery (selected tags) and blocked tags, which remove content from view.
    GalleryService
    Provides access to the viral/top/best galleries.
    ImageService
    Services related to manipulating images in Imgur (why we're here, assumedly)
    MemeService
    API services for memes.
    NotificationService
    Access user-specific notifications
    Quota
    Provides insight into quota status for a given client account.
    TopicService
    API service for topics, which provide access to categorized content like "funny" and "aww."
